        </h2>
        <h2 class="mb-8 hidden text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-200 md:block playfair-display-reg">
          Unlock the door to intelligent, worry-free monetary management.
        </h2>
        <div class="flex justify-center gap-2">
          <button class="btn btn-warning dark:bg-blue-300 dark:border-gray-800" onclick="window.location.href='/login'">
